Package org.opennars.io

Input/output management

All Narsese-based input/output interfaces of the system are defined in this package.

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Parser
    abstraction for parsing of narsese
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ConfigReader
    Used to read and parse the XML configuration file
    Narsese

    Symbols  
    Texts
